NT||lb|*bWhat would you bid?^^2s|mb|2s|nt|
^b@22S is the best bid. You could conceivably end up playing in a 7-card fit at the 3 level but that is extremely unlikely. Partner is almost certainly short in spades making it very likely he or she has 4+ clubs. Therefore, 2S is very clear and low risk.|
